# Project: Selenium Automated Testing Framework

This repository presents a professional-grade web testing framework designed as a portfolio project to illustrate strong test automation skills in Python and Selenium.

- Utilizes the Page Object Model for scalable and maintainable architecture
- Includes centralized error handling with automatic screenshot capture on test failures
- Features robust explicit waits for dynamic web pages and thorough inline documentation

## Technologies
- Python 3.x
- Selenium WebDriver
- ChromeDriver

## Project Highlights
- Comprehensive test coverage of core e-commerce features (profile, home, products, cart)
- All-in-one runner for seamless automated smoke/regression testing
- Clean code, modular design, and extensibility recommended in industry best practices
- Includes detailed comments and documentation for easy understanding
- Designed to be easily extended with additional test cases or page objects